msg: Fix a test error introduced in the merge performed in r33484.
On trunk svntest.actions.run_and_verify_svn() now returns the exit code, along
with the output and error text.  The test merged over from trunk assumed this
behavior, but 1.5.x only returns the output and error text.  This patch just
removes the extra return value from the test.
